data.description: Welcome Home to this phenomenal home with a historical story. This four/five bedroom home has so much space.   The inviting living room welcomes plenty of sunshine and features a wall to ceiling custom stone fireplace. The espresso flooring brings even more attention to the fireplace. Dinner for 12? No problem in your formal dining room with bay window and opens to the front porch. Enjoy the granite counter space, custom tile and breakfast bar area with space for 4 barstools in the kitchen and appliances stay. 2018 brought a new roof, a 3+ car garage featuring a workshop and plenty of storage.  The home highlights include extra wide footboards and gorgeous custom trim work, newer garage doors, newer asphalt driveways to the front of the home, 3 full custom designed bathrooms with glass shower doors an amazing built in (a must see)! This gorgeous Colonial has an all season treated grass, offering an amazing curb appeal. Relax on a newly designed back porch overlooking a perfectly maintained fenced in back yard with hot tub and pergola..  Finished walk out lower level features another full bathroom. Whole house water proofing was done in May of 2023, whole house water treatment  and reverse osmosis in kitchen. New hot water tank and concrete patio was added in 2020.  The front porch was rebuilt in May of 2023 with composite decking!! New direct vent hot water tank installed 2023.  A must see! Want to know the historical story? Find out during your personal showing.
